# Login & Signup App üîê

## Project Description
This project implements a Login and Signup application using Firebase Authentication.

## Features
- Email & Password Signup
- Login functionality
- Form validation and error messages
- Password reset option
- Protected profile page (only for logged-in users)
- Logout functionality
- Optional Google Sign-In

## Technologies Used
- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript
- Firebase Authentication

## How to Run
1. Clone the repository
2. Open `index.html` in a browser
3. Configure Firebase credentials

